<a href="/questions/140381-when-do-we-see-the-movie">When do we see the movie</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_140381'><a id="like_count_community_question_140381" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/140381?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">9 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F9917938-blood-red-road">like</a></span>

