</a><br/><br/>If you&apos;re cool with those things, then I got to say <b>YOU HAFTA READ THIS!</b><br/><br/>When I started reading Blood Red Road I did not like it that much because the beginning was a little bit cheesy especially when they talked about stars and prophecy. Also, the writing style d</span>
