        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2174679665" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13600146078067824411">As usual I’m very late to the party, but I really enjoyed this! It features a hate to love done in the way I actually enjoy it (aka the right way), a deeply flawed MC who is called out on her issues, adventure, and bringing down an evil government.<br/>The writing was a bit hard to get into at first because of how it’s written (slang, no quotation marks for speaking) but once I was hooked I HAD to finish.</span>

          </span>
